00:00:51.159 --> 00:00:52.079
This Dragon's Roar...

00:00:52.439 --> 00:00:53.719
I don't know how to do it either.

00:00:54.119 --> 00:00:54.920
I don't.

00:00:55.240 --> 00:00:57.079
