00:00:57.439 --> 00:00:58.280
that you are...

00:00:58.520 --> 00:00:59.399
twenty years ago...

00:00:59.479 --> 00:01:00.679
the one who swept through Southeast Asia...

00:01:00.719 --> 00:01:02.640
the billiard world's The Phantom Artisan?

00:01:03.200 --> 00:01:04.599
And you can't even do Dragon's Roar?

00:01:06.359 --> 00:01:07.400
Oh my.

00:01:08.680 --> 00:01:10.599
Back then, I was hunted by enemies...

00:01:11.079 --> 00:01:12.079
and nearly lost my life.

00:01:12.079 --> 00:01:13.079
Only then did I realize...

00:01:13.680 --> 00:01:14.840
true skill...

00:01:15.200 --> 00:01:16.599
