00:01:16.879 --> 00:01:18.319
Steady in chaotic times...

00:01:18.640 --> 00:01:20.680
unmoved by the currents.

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:22.040
Any external help...

00:01:22.280 --> 00:01:23.959
is just an illusion.

00:01:24.480 --> 00:01:25.319
If you want to win...

00:01:26.040 --> 00:01:27.920
you must walk your own path.

00:01:28.359 --> 00:01:29.560
You said all that...

00:01:29.959 --> 00:01:32.319
but you still don't know the Seventh Move of the Heavenly Craft, do you?

00:01:32.599 --> 00:01:34.920
That is your Senior Brother's exclusive secret technique.

00:01:36.079 --> 00:01:36.959
If you want to ask...

00:01:37.359 --> 00:01:38.439
go ask him.

00:01:42.439 --> 00:01:43.120
Senior Brother.

00:01:43.319 --> 00:01:44.680
Just teach me, please.

00:01:45.519 --> 00:01:46.519
No matter how I teach you...

00:01:46.519 --> 00:01:47.760
