00:01:47.959 --> 00:01:49.319
You have to learn to play your own game.

00:01:50.079 --> 00:01:50.599
Do you understand?

00:01:51.239 --> 00:01:51.920
You just don't want to teach.

00:01:52.040 --> 00:01:53.319
I don't want to learn it anyway.

00:01:53.680 --> 00:01:55.439
I will definitely play better shots.

00:01:59.879 --> 00:02:00.480
Hei Ba.

